sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Budget
  participant BudgetService
  participant PieChartBudget
  participant BudgetCard
  participant Router

  User->>Budget: Open Budget Screen
  Budget->>BudgetService: Fetch Budgets (getBudgets)
  BudgetService-->>Budget: Return Budgets Data
  Budget->>PieChartBudget: Display Pie Chart
  Budget->>BudgetCard: Display Budget List
  User->>Budget: Press Back Button
  Budget->>Router: Navigate to Home Screen